= About =

Content management system for electronic journal. Used on http://chemphys.edu.ru/ (Physical and chemical kinetics in gas dynamics)


= Features =

* Multilanguage (ru/en) content: user-submitted articles, journal pages, ui etc
* User registration/authentication via e-mail
* Article submission: mechanism for adding authors, organization
* Article review process - multiple reviewwers per article, general resolution, rework process


= Dependencies =

* Django 1.7+
